      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you're not a doctor but i'm just trying to understand the math behind it. like, if someone had a sensitivity factor of 50 (meaning 1 unit drops them 50 points), how many units would they need to go from 185 down to 100? i just want to see how the formula works so i can do it myself next time.",
